snippet.title: Princess Fun Place
snippet.description:
Family friendly entertainment for all who like to play with cool toys including Barbie toys, Disney Princess castles and playsets, Peppa Pig, Shopkins, Tsum Tsum, My Little Pony toys, and reveal surprises from variety of blind bags. We are going to make slime, create cool art and craft projects, prepare yummy Princess snacks, and play stories with new popular Peppa Pig, Disney Princess, and Barbie toys for you. Enjoy!

New story with new awesome toys every week!!!
